    "text": "The best eel bowls in Osaka, Japan at  @hozenji_yamakazu  This unagi master has been grilling unagi for over 30 years and serves the best eel bowls! They have multiple different bowls ranging from the full eel bowl to the eel and salmon roe combo, and my personal favorite the eel and uni combo. Definitely a must try if you\u2019re in Osaka Japan!   Location: \ud83d\udccdHozenji Yamakazu 1 Chome-1-16 Nanba, Chuo Ward, Osaka, 542-0076  Number: \ud83d\udcde 06-6211-5800 - - - - - - - - #japan #japanese #japanesefood #donabe #rice #japantravel #japantrip #japanstyle #japanlover #japanfood #unagi #japanesefoods #japon #nippon",
